---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import BattleCry from '../components/BattleCry.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
    {JSON.stringify({
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'Organization',
      name: 'Journal Foundation',
      url: 'https://journalfoundation.org',
      publishingPrinciples: 'https://journalfoundation.org/privacy'
    })}
  </script>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <BattleCry>
    <div class="hero-quote">
      <p><strong>Mark Zuckerberg and Elon Musk have their clutches in us</strong>‚Äîtightening the screws while we bleed on the mat.</p>
      <p>Every screen, every algorithm, every "curated" feed is training you to be a biological robot for advertisers.</p>
      <p>When robots come with smiling faces, every 10th sentence an ad‚Äîit's lights out for human free thought and diversity.</p>
      <p><strong>We're building the escape route.</strong></p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="cta-group">
      <a href="/docs/quickstart" class="cta cta-primary">
        üõ†Ô∏è Run a Cypherlot
      </a>
      <a href="/about" class="cta cta-secondary">
        üì¢ Join the Movement
      </a>
      <a href="/governance" class="cta cta-tertiary">
        üí∞ Support the Foundation
      </a>
    </div>
  </BattleCry>
  
  <!-- Three Part Explainer -->
  <section class="explainer-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why This Matters</h2>
        <p class="subtitle">We're not building another app. We're building the foundation for digital sovereignty.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="explainer-grid">
        <div class="explainer-card">
          <div class="explainer-number">1</div>
          <h3>The Problem</h3>
          <p>We're living in a monoculture controlled by algorithmic manipulation:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Facebook feeds controlled by Zuckerberg</li>
            <li>Twitter weaponized by Musk</li>
            <li>TikTok optimizing for addiction</li>
            <li>Every screen training us to be puppets</li>
            <li>The boa constrictor keeps tightening</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="explainer-card">
          <div class="explainer-number">2</div>
          <h3>Why Decentralization Failed</h3>
          <p>Mastodon, Diaspora, Fediverse‚Äîthey decentralized but didn't anonymize:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Metadata still exposed:</strong> Who talks to whom is visible</li>
            <li><strong>Federation centralizes:</strong> Your instance admin sees everything</li>
            <li><strong>Correlation attacks:</strong> Traffic patterns reveal identity</li>
            <li><strong>No plausible deniability:</strong> Encrypted data can be seized</li>
            <li><strong>The China problem:</strong> Download now, decrypt with quantum later</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="explainer-card">
          <div class="explainer-number">3</div>
          <h3>The Cypherlots Difference</h3>
          <p>Infrastructure for sovereignty, not another social network:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Encrypted by default, not optional</li>
            <li>Capability-based sharing (scoped, revocable)</li>
            <li>Metadata minimization through blind relays</li>
            <li>Self-hostable without sacrifice</li>
            <li>Your data in YOUR basement</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Urgency -->
  <section class="urgency-section">
    <div class="container urgency-content">
      <h2>The Stakes Are Existential</h2>
      
      <div class="urgency-quote">
        <p>We're not breathing. We're just getting squeezed.</p>
        
        <p>All our screens, all the time, giving us algorithmic manipulation. The top 10 on Netflix. The news feeds. Even the music. <strong>It's called the monoculture.</strong></p>
        
        <p>Right now it's a screen next to us. Soon it's a smiling face‚Äîyour best friend‚Äîand every 10th sentence is an advertisement.</p>
        
        <p>The hypnotism by robots is coming, whether we act or not.</p>
        
        <p><strong>If we don't create this free, radical way for humans to have THEIR OWN robots‚Äîthen it's lights out for human free thought and diversity. It's a new dark ages.</strong></p>
      </div>
      
      <p class="urgency-conclusion">That's why Cypherlots exist. That's why this foundation exists.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Get Started -->
  <section class="get-started-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Get Started</h2>
        <p class="subtitle">Three ways to join the resistance</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="explainer-grid">
        <div class="explainer-card">
          <h3>üõ†Ô∏è For Developers</h3>
          <p>Run a Cypherlot in under 60 seconds:</p>
          <pre><code>docker run -d --name cypherlot \
  -p 443:443 \
  -v $HOME/cypherlot:/data \
  ghcr.io/journalfoundation/cypherlot:0.1</code></pre>
          <p class="card-link"><a href="/docs/quickstart">View full documentation ‚Üí</a></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="explainer-card">
          <h3>üì¢ For Advocates</h3>
          <p>Help build the movement:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Share the battle cry</li>
            <li>Join community discussions</li>
            <li>Download advocacy toolkit</li>
            <li>Speak at events</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="card-link"><a href="/community">Join the conversation ‚Üí</a></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="explainer-card">
          <h3>üí∞ For Funders</h3>
          <p>Support the foundation:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Fund specification development</li>
            <li>Sponsor security audits</li>
            <li>Enable advocacy work</li>
            <li>Support open source</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="card-link"><a href="/governance#funding">View transparency dashboard ‚Üí</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Cypherlots Explainer -->
  <section class="cypherlots-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>What Is a Cypherlot?</h2>
        <p class="subtitle">A personal, encrypted data node that lets you share exactly what you intend‚Äîwith no platform in the middle.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="cypherlots-content">
        <p class="intro">A <strong>Cypherlot</strong> is a privacy primitive for people, not platforms:</p>
        
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>
            <span class="checkmark">‚úì</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Encrypted by default:</strong> All data is encrypted at rest and in transit
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="checkmark">‚úì</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Capability-based sharing:</strong> Grant scoped, expiring, revocable access
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="checkmark">‚úì</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Metadata minimization:</strong> Blind relays that can't read your data
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="checkmark">‚úì</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Self-hostable:</strong> Run it on a Raspberry Pi in your basement
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="checkmark">‚úì</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Not a platform:</strong> It's infrastructure‚Äîapps interoperate without surveillance
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        
        <blockquote class="founder-quote">
          "Your data in your basement, not Zuckerberg's data center. That's the whole point."
        </blockquote>
        
        <div class="cta-group" style="justify-content: center; margin-top: var(--space-xl);">
          <a href="/cypherlots" class="cta cta-secondary">Learn More About Cypherlots ‚Üí</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero Quote */
  .hero-quote {
    background: var(--void-lighter);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--urgent-amber);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    margin: var(--space-xl) auto;
    max-width: 900px;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2.5vw, 1.375rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  
  .hero-quote p {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .hero-quote p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  
  .hero-quote strong {
    color: var(--encrypted-green);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  /* CTAs */
  .cta-group {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .cta-primary {
    background: var(--encrypted-green);
    color: var(--void);
  }
  
  .cta-primary:hover {
    background: #0D9668;
    color: var(--void);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
  }
  
  .cta-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    border-color: var(--electric-blue);
    color: var(--electric-blue);
  }
  
  .cta-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--electric-blue);
    color: var(--void);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  .cta-tertiary {
    background: transparent;
    border-color: var(--text-muted);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  
  .cta-tertiary:hover {
    border-color: var(--text-primary);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  /* Sections */
  section {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--void-lighter);
  }
  
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .section-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  /* Explainer Grid */
  .explainer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  .explainer-card {
    background: var(--void-lighter);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }
  
  .explainer-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--encrypted-green);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }
  
  .explainer-number {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--void);
    border: 2px solid var(--encrypted-green);
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--encrypted-green);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .explainer-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--encrypted-green);
  }
  
  .explainer-card ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .explainer-card li {
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  
  .explainer-card li::before {
    content: "‚Üí";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--electric-blue);
  }
  
  .explainer-card pre {
    background: var(--void);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }
  
  .explainer-card code {
    color: var(--encrypted-green);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }
  
  .card-link {
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  /* Urgency Section */
  .urgency-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1), rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1));
    border-left: 4px solid var(--urgent-amber);
  }
  
  .urgency-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .urgency-content h2 {
    color: var(--urgent-amber);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .urgency-quote {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  
  .urgency-quote p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .urgency-conclusion {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  /* Cypherlots Section */
  .cypherlots-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .intro {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }
  
  .feature-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  
  .checkmark {
    color: var(--encrypted-green);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .feature-list strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .founder-quote {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--void-lighter);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--electric-blue);
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  
  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cta-group {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }
    
    .cta {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>